title Adding new note with single page version

browser->server: HTTP POST https://fullstack-exampleapp.herokuapp.com/new_note_spa

note over server:
Server starts executing code
that saves new note and adds it to /data.json
end note

server-->browser: [{ content: "Added a new note", date: "2019-09-22" }, ...]

note over browser:
browser executes the event handler
that renders only new note to display
end note